{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"HTMLStyleElement","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLStyleElement","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLStyleElement\"><code>HTMLStyleElement</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>プロパティ</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLStyleElement/media\"><code>media</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLStyleElement/scoped\"><code>scoped</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLStyleElement/type\"><code>type</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>継承</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement\"><code>HTMLElement</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Element\"><code>Element</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Node\"><code>Node</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p><code>HTMLStyleElement</code> インタフェースは <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/HTML/Element/style\"><code>&lt;style&gt;</code></a> 要素を表すインタフェースです。<a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement\"><code>HTMLElement</code></a> と <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLLinkElement\"><code>LinkStyle</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> のプロパティとメソッドを継承しています。</p>\n\n<p>This interface doesn't allow to manipulate the CSS it contains (in most case). To manipulate CSS, see <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSS_Object_Model/Using_dynamic_styling_information\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Using dynamic styling information (en-US)</a> for an overview of the objects used to manipulate specified CSS properties using the DOM.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"properties","title":"プロパティ","isH3":false,"content":"<p><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement\"><code>HTMLElement</code></a> および <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLLinkElement\"><code>LinkStyle</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> から継承するプロパティの他に、以下の固有プロパティを持ちます。</p>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"htmlstyleelement.media\"><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLStyleElement/media\"><code>HTMLStyleElement.media</code></a></dt>\n <dd>スタイル情報の適用先として意図するメディアを表す <a href=\"/ja/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String_6fa58bba0570d663099f0ae7ae8883ab\"><code>DOMString</code></a></dd>\n <dt id=\"htmlstyleelement.type_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLStyleElement/type\"><code>HTMLStyleElement.type</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>この style 要素のスタイルの種類を表す <a href=\"/ja/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String_6fa58bba0570d663099f0ae7ae8883ab\"><code>DOMString</code></a></dd>\n <dt id=\"htmlstyleelement.disabled\"><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"この項目についての文書はまだ書かれていません。書いてみませんか？\"><code>HTMLStyleElement.disabled</code></a></dt>\n <dd><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Boolean\"><code>Boolean</code></a>。スタイルシート有効時には <code>true</code> 、無効時には <code>false</code> を返す。</dd>\n <dt id=\"htmlstyleelement.scoped_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLStyleElement/scoped\"><code>HTMLStyleElement.scoped</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Boolean\"><code>Boolean</code></a>。スタイルの適用対象が文書全体の場合は <code>false</code>、 <code>scoped</code> 属性により適用範囲が制限されている場合は <code>true</code> を返す。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"methods","title":"メソッド","isH3":false,"content":"<p>固有のメソッドは持ちません。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specifications","title":"仕様","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">仕様書</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">策定状況</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">コメント</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/semantics.html#the-style-element\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML Living Standard<br><small lang=\"ja\">HTMLStyleElement の定義</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">現行の標準</span></td>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/html52/\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" title=\"HTML5の仕様書\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML5</a> より変更無し</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/html52/document-metadata.html#the-style-element\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML5<br><small lang=\"ja\">HTMLStyleElement の定義</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">勧告</span></td>\n   <td><code>scoped</code> プロパティの追加</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/DOM-Level-2-HTML/html.html#ID-16428977\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Document Object Model (DOM) Level 2 HTML Specification<br><small lang=\"ja\">HTMLStyleElement の定義</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-obsolete\">廃止</span></td>\n   <td><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLLinkElement\"><code>LinkStyle</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> インタフェースからの継承の追加</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/REC-DOM-Level-1/level-one-html.html#ID-16428977\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Document Object Model (DOM) Level 1 Specification<br><small lang=\"ja\">HTMLStyleElement の定義</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-obsolete\">廃止</span></td>\n   <td>最初期の定義</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"ブラウザ実装状況","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"api.HTMLStyleElement","dataURL":"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLStyleElement/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect2\">\n\n\n<p></p><p></p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"関連情報","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/HTML/Element/style\"><code>&lt;style&gt;</code></a> - <code>HTMLStyleElement</code> インタフェースを持つ HTML 要素</li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSS_Object_Model/Using_dynamic_styling_information\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">動的スタイル情報の利用 (en-US)</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"プロパティ","id":"properties"},{"text":"メソッド","id":"methods"},{"text":"仕様","id":"specifications"},{"text":"ブラウザ実装状況","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"関連情報","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"HTMLStyleElement インタフェースは <style> 要素を表すインタフェースです。HTMLElement と LinkStyle (en-US) のプロパティとメソッドを継承しています。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"HTMLStyleElement","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"HTMLStyleElement","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"style","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"HTMLStyleElement","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/web/api/htmlstyleelement","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/web/api/htmlstyleelement/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web","title":"開発者向けのウェブ技術"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLStyleElement","title":"HTMLStyleElement"}],"pageTitle":"HTMLStyleElement - Web API | MDN","noIndexing":false}}